                <h1>Effortlessly Start Programs with Task Manager</h1>
                <p>To start a program in Task Manager, right-click the taskbar and select "Task Manager." Click "File" in the top-left corner, then choose "Run new task." Type the desired program's name and click "OK." This method allows for quick access to applications, enhancing productivity by managing tasks efficiently in Windows.</p>
